SYNOPSIS
  wr [options]

  wr, a webring server backend.

OPTIONS
  -h, --help              Show this help and exit.
  -v, --version           Show the version and exit.

SERVER OPTIONS
  -l, --listen=<...>      URL to listen on, like http://0.0.0.0:8000 (required).
  -d, --database=<...>    Path to the sqlite database (required).
  -w, --web-root=<...>    Directory of the built frontend (required).
  -u, --public-url=<...>  Public base URL for the OAuth redirect (required).

DEBUG OPTIONS
  -L, --log-file=<...>    Append the log to FILE instead of standard error.
  -V, --verbose           Log at debug verbosity, including the per-request
                          access lines.
  -D, --dev               Run in dev mode with a login bypass for an admin and a
                          user.
